ion\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>브라우저 터치스크린 액션</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">touch-action</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pan-y pinch-zoom<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> 다중 지정 가능</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Values</th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">auto</td>\n<td align=\"left\">default</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">none</td>\n<td align=\"left\">모든 터치 이벤트 무시</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">pan-x <br> pan-y <br> pan-left <br> pan-right <br> pan-up <br> pan-down</td>\n<td align=\"left\">특정 축, 방향</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">pinch-zoom</td>\n<td align=\"left\">손가락 사용한 확대, 축소</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n<h3>Mobile (iOS)</h3>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Values</th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">텍스트 자동 확대 방지</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">-webkit-touch-callout: none</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">텍스트, 이미지 길게 누를 때 : 제한적으로만 사용하기</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">구버전 스크롤링</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">height: 100dvh</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">동적 뷰포트 기준 height</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token function\">env</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>safe-area-inset-bottom<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\